 Notorious is a fast-paced show revolving around the lives of two friends who use each other s professional positions to get what they want. Julia is a producer of the highest rated news show and her friend Jake is a criminal defence lawyer. The two use each other to their advantage. For instance, Julia will use Jake s clients to get expos s and high ratings, and Jake will use the show to influence the public on his cases. The show gives an insightful view of how news is created to influence public opinion. Star Rating: 3.5/5